# GitNexus enforcement

## North star

> **Prefer graph + embeddings when the index is fresh. Use `query` for fuzzy/exploratory reasoning (BM25 + vectors). Refresh autonomously when stale or embeddings are missing. Classical tools only when GN is stale/failing/wrong — say why.**

Local LLM / zero token cost: rebuild context freely; do not skip gates for speed.

## Graph + embeddings (not graph-only)

| Need | Tool | Why |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Fuzzy concept, flow, "how does X work?" | `query` | Hybrid BM25 + **embedding** vectors (RRF) |
| One symbol, callers, 360° | `context` | Structural graph |
| Pre-edit blast radius | `impact` | Graph traversal |
| Pre-commit / done | `detect_changes` | Diff → processes |

**Anti-pattern:** jumping straight to `context`/`impact`/`grep` for exploratory work — that skips embeddings. `SemanticSearch` is blocked; use `query` instead.

Refresh always includes `--embeddings` (`gitnexus:refresh` / `agent-refresh`). Missing embeddings = stale (same as commit behind).

## MCP defaults (generous — local LLM)

Run hook copy-paste calls verbatim; expand freely when needed:

| Tool | Default | Notes |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `context` | `include_content: false` | Need body → Read offset/limit |
| `query` | `limit: 5`, `max_symbols: 12` | Primary semantic+graph orient tool |
| `impact` | `summaryOnly: false`, `limit: 100` | Full blast radius before edits |
| `detect_changes` | `scope: unstaged` | Pre-commit → `staged`; PR → `compare` |

## Session (autonomous Shell)

`npm run gitnexus:agent-brief` or READ `gitnexus://repo/__GITNEXUS_REPO__/context`. Stale or missing embeddings → `npm run gitnexus:agent-refresh` (`required_permissions: ["all"]`). Never ask user to analyze.

## Gates (do not skip)

```
1. brief OR context — session start
2. query — fuzzy / explore / orient (graph + embeddings)
3. context → process — drill into symbols
4. impact upstream — before runtime source edits
5. detect_changes — before commit / done
```

HIGH/CRITICAL impact → warn before proceeding.

## When fresh — hooks block

Symbol grep → `context`. SemanticSearch/broad Glob → `query`. Large source Read → `query` → `context` → Read offset/limit.

## Fallback

Stale, missing embeddings, refresh failed, GN wrong after `uid` retry, MCP down — classical OK; one-sentence why.

